moji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係拍案叫絕"},{"pid":"8462e6fcc2589f346d62379d52cc6c3891ed391a","tid":593180,"uid":149055,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:12:07.000Z","msg":"我有100蚊 ，你多我一半:你有150蚊<br />\n                     你多我一倍:你有200蚊<br />\n  <br />\n正常logic: 你多我三倍，你有400蚊<br />\n連登小學雞:你多我三倍，即係是我3倍，即係300蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6e19c65b81f8c1f9c04775c6347fa287a73c87","tid":593180,"uid":5310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"本來同樓主無怨無仇，但最可笑嘅係樓主因為出題者比出嘅所謂<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正確</span></span>答案，繼而猜想出題者嘅諗法，而去否定根據題目意思而計出黎嘅答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再講啦，16呢個答案就算你改做哥哥比阿梅年紀大兩倍時，求哥哥的年齡，咪一樣錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本就係出題者自己都搞唔清楚個問題，比出左4個選擇，1個所謂<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正確</span></span>答案，到底係邊個話出題者一定啱？<br />\n<br />\n我都係廢撚事同小六程度都無嘅人嘈，教精你都哂氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffd5bf2af065d2bdbe797e6eb55e8d6b34ebe10","tid":593180,"uid":11388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23602edcdf99cbc8c23bcddcbb68ee441d8689e0","tid":593180,"uid":5310,"like":9,"dislike":25,"score":-16,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T20:48:54.000Z","msg":"現時阿梅4歲，哥哥比佢大3倍，即現時哥哥=4*4=16歲，設經過y年後<br />\n3(4+y)=16+y<br />\n12+3y=16+y<br />\n2y=4<br />\ny=2<br />\n即阿梅6歲，哥哥18歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c